###orchard 引入js/css/font


>添加js


1.  在Orchard.Web\Themes\TheThemeMachine\Views\Layout.cshtml 添加路径
```js
Script.Include(Url.Content("~/Themes/TheThemeMachine/Scripts/base.js"));
```

2. 在Orchard.Web\Themes\TheThemeMachine\Scripts\新建Web.config 添加权限

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<configuration>
    <system.webServer>
        <staticContent>
            <clientCache cacheControlMode="UseMaxAge" cacheControlMaxAge="7.00:00:00" />
        </staticContent>
        <handlers accessPolicy="Script,Read">
            <!-- For any request to a file exists on disk, return it via native http module. AccessPolicy="Script" above is to allow for a managed 404 page. -->
            <add name="StaticFile" path="*" verb="*" modules="StaticFileModule" preCondition="integratedMode" resourceType="File" requireAccess="Read" />
        </handlers>
    </system.webServer>
</configuration>

```
---
>添加 css

1. 在Orchard.Web\Themes\TheThemeMachine\Views\Layout.cshtml 添加路径
```js
Style.Include("bootstrap.css");
```

2. 添加 Web.config 
---

>添加 woff2

1. 在Orchard.Web\Themes\TheThemeMachine\Views\Layout.cshtml 添加路径
```js
Style.Include(Url.Content("~/Themes/TheThemeMachine/fonts/glyphicons-halflings-regular.woff2"));
```

2. 添加 Web.config


---

> TheThemeMachine tree

```
│  Placement.info
